snippet.title: WELDIVER  -  Official Trailer - One of the World’s Deadliest Jobs 🤿!
snippet.description:
My Job........Diver Underwater Welding... 🤿

Welcome to my world. Weldiver
I chose the most dangerous job in the world. Not because I wanted to, but because someone has to. I’m an Underwater Welder. One meter down, you lose 1% of your chance to survive. I live on the edge of life and death. It's not just a job. It's a life... a battle... a fight for survival.

Wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3299160
If you want to join our community and stay in close contact with the developers, hop onto our official Discord server: https://discord.gg/Hzd3WbFRxk
X: https://x.com/Weldivergame
